title: #36 Drop It, Airplane Mode (A Make Up Podcast)

description:
Between You & Nikki, she got the message regarding her tone, which turned out to be the stress she felt having to perform in front of a major name in comedy. Both Nikki and Andrew slept great because they made up in the car. Andrew reports about apps that drain your phone battery, a brave 11 year old and Tim Tebow in You Heard It Here First. They sort through bestie messages in Listener Mail and in the Final Thought, they discuss Nikki's latest date.
